---
import Section from '@components/Section.astro';
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Roadmap | Degenerous" page="Roadmap">
	<main>
		<Section gap>
            <h1>Roadmap</h1>

            <ul>
                <li>Distribute Inception Arks on raresama.com</li>
                <li>Launch the tokengated chat</li>
                <li>Elect board members (10 NeYons + 5 new ones)</li>
                <li>Start planning the service trip and distribution of $125 000 to charity</li>
                <li>Launch governance</li>
                <li>Reveal the art of the starting 1k Potentials (avatars)</li>
                <li>Launch storyline-focused gaming & metaverse events</li>
                <li>Airdrop Choice Card NFTs</li>
                <li>Launch products - trait-gated Governance, ChatBot, and Evolver/Customizer</li>
                <li>Allow burning of Choice Card NFTs along with Imaginarion</li>
            </ul>

            <p>At Degenerous DAO , we strive to revolutionize charity and NFTs. Our end goal is to build an NFT-governed decentralized platform that allows donors to directly fund verified meaningful causes and gives creators the power to guarantee efficient resource allocation. Our mission is to foster trust, transparency and collaboration in the industry to facilitate positive change in communities and create global impact.</p>
        </Section>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style lang="scss">
    ul {
        position: relative;
        list-style: none;
        margin-left: 2rem;

        li{
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;

            margin-left: -3px;
            padding-left: 2rem;

            &::before, &::after {
                content: "";
                position: absolute;
                left: -.2rem;
                top: 50%;
                translate: 0 -50%;

                height: 1rem;
                aspect-ratio: 1/1;
                border-radius: 50%;

                background-color: white;
            }

            &:after {
                background-color: hsl(var(--bg-color));

                left: -0.05rem;
                height: .75rem;
            }
        }

        &::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset-block: -1rem;
            width: .2rem;
            background: white;
        }
    }

    p {
        margin-top: 4rem;
    }
</style>
